      • rowDisplayer

        static java.lang.String rowDisplayer​(java.util.List<java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​java.lang.Integer>> list,
                                     java.lang.String prefix)
        Generates a string representing a table. Adds spaces as padding, '|' as separator and NewLine character for new line (\n).
        Parameters:
        list - - List of Maps. The First key of each map will render as first in each column, which becomes a row. The second key will be the second line in each column, which is the second row, and so on.
        prefix - - String to prepend to column value.
        Returns:
        String
